==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Traditionalism
<hw>Tra*di"tion*al*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A system of
faith founded on tradition; esp., the doctrine that all religious faith
is to be based solely upon what is delivered from competent authority,
exclusive of rational processes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traditionalist</ent>⟦br⟧
